{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cb4aba08f0","title":"对南京军区党委关于是否派军队支持造反派的请示报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7e10fd14d8","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":21,"articleId":"cb4aba08f0"}],"tags":[{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"9e10ed09e5","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革小组1967年1月23日发出了《关于人民解放军坚决支持革命左派群众的决定》"}],"contents":[{"id":"70aa4b08a5","type":"title","text":"对南京军区党委关于是否派军队支持造反派的请示报告\"的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"9e10ed09e5","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"ee6bf9d9a3","type":"paragraph","text":"立派军队支持左派广大群众。请的处","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"4b06cc25f8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"907f428ed2","type":"paragraph","text":"一月廿一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"0bf00af831","type":"paragraph","text":"以后凡有真正革命派要求军队支持、援助，都应当这样做。所请不介入，是假的，早已介入了。此事似应重新发出命令回，以前命令作废。请的。又及","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"1f7b41778c","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]中国人民解放军南京军区党委1967年1月21日向中共中央军委副主席林彪并中央军委报告说，“硕接安徽军区报告，首都第三造反司令部驻安徽联络站等单位向安徽军区提出，廿二日到廿三日，在合肥召开15万到20万人大会”，“要安徽军区派出三百到五百名部队警卫会场。他们提出，如派部队就是支持文化大革命，如不派就是不支持文化大革命，并限安徽军区廿一日十四时前答复。是否派部队，请速指示”","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"}],"page":{"id":"1622118390","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0","start":276,"end":276}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2fe389cd8f","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"397b7ac765","type":"paragraph","text":"应派军队支持左派广大群众。请酌处。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"9d50ffad6c","type":"title","text":"对南京军区党委关于是否派军队支持造反派的请示报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"d76d717d5d","type":"paragraph","text":"以后凡有真正革命派要求军队支持、援助，都应当这样做。所谓不介入，是假的，早已介入了。此事似应重新发出命令，以前命令作废。请酌。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"}],"page":{"id":"e5149f407c","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"cb4aba08f0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}